window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Ce'Anna and her husband, Trent, are nearing their sixth anniversary of marriage. Ever since they said \"I do\", their romance was like a whirlwind. That is, until Ce'Anna's first secret. Then her second. </p> <p>Life is going crazy, and things are starting to \"get real\". Tensions continue to rise, until Ce'Anna is placed in a situation where she has to make a choice between the one she truly loves, and the one she's not sure about.</p>"; 
